CallCtrAgentFavTrfrDest.name: CallCtrAgentFavTrfrDest
CallCtrAgentFavTrfrDest.description: Represents a transfer destination that has been marked (starred) as a favorite in the Omni-Channel softphone by a contact center agent for voice call transfers.

AgentId.description: The unique ID of the contact center agent who marked the transfer destination as a favorite.

CallCenterId.description: The unique ID of the contact center from where the agent starred the transfer destination as a favorite.

Name.description: The name of the transfer destination record that’s marked as a favorite.

OwnerId.description: The unique ID of the user who owns this object.

TransferDestination.description: The unique ID of the transfer destination that’s marked as a favorite. This is an external ID.
